Class OrderContract.OrderSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clover.sdk.v3.order.OrderContract.OrderSummary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseColumns, OrderContract.OrderSummaryColumns
    Enclosing class:
    OrderContract

    public static final class OrderContract.OrderSummary
extends Object
implements BaseColumns, OrderContract.OrderSummaryColumns
    Provides order summaries for up to 100 days of recent orders. To retrieve full order data use the OrderConnector.
